Building Zcashdarklite

See doc/readme-qt.rst for instructions on building Zcashdarklite-Qt,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Zcashdarklite.

See doc/build-*.txt for instructions on building zcashdarklited,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Zcashdarklite.
